voxtype (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add optional GPU acceleration (Vulkan, CUDA, Metal, HIP)
  * Upgrade whisper-rs to 0.15.1 for latest features
  * Fix Arch PKGBUILD build dependencies (cmake, pkgconf)
